<div class="info-banner research-and-development-banner-bg">
  <div class="info-banner-title info-title">
    <h1>R&D</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="">
  <div class="bg-light-color pr of-hidden">
    <%= image_tag "cf-logo-outline-white", class: "white-logo-bg" %>
    <div class="content-card card-reverse pr">
      <div class="card-image-area">
        <%= image_tag "research-and-development/r-and-d-team", alt: "alttext", class: "card-image w100" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h4 class="text-larger text-bold">R&D Team</h4>
          <p>CF PharmTech R&D team is made up of scientists with successful experience in the research and development of inhaled drugs and many experienced senior research and development personnel.</p>
          <p>Relying on the international and domestic top academic and regulatory exchanges and technical cooperation, our R&D team has the professional knowledge and skills, capable of carrying out a full range of respiratory system drug delivery technology research and development work, to provide high-quality inhaled products for the global market.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-offwhite">
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-image-area w35">
        <%= image_tag "research-and-development/therapeutic-areas", alt: "alttext", class: "card-image w65" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area w65">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h4 class="text-larger text-bold teal-text">Therapeutic Areas</h4>
          <p>CF PharmTech focuses on the development of nasal and pulmonary delivery technology for respiratory disease treatments, including:</p>
          <ul class="bulleted-list text-large">
            <li><%= link_to "Asthma", "#{therapeutic_areas_path}#Asthma", class: "teal-text" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "COPD", "#{therapeutic_areas_path}#COPD", class: "teal-text" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Rhinitis", "#{therapeutic_areas_path}#Rhinitis", class: "teal-text" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Other Respiratory Diseases", "#{therapeutic_areas_path}#Other-Respiratory-Diseases", class: "teal-text" %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-image-area w35">
        <%= image_tag "research-and-development/dosage-forms", alt: "alttext", class: "card-image w65" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area w65">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h4 class="text-larger text-bold teal-text">Dosage Forms</h4>
          <p>CF PharmTech has a complete R&D platforms and manufacturing capabilities for the following dosage forms:</p>
          <ul class="bulleted-list text-large">
            <li><%= link_to "Metered Dose Inhaler (MDI)", "#{dosage_forms_path}#MDI", class: "teal-text" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Dry Powder Inhaler (DPI)", "#{dosage_forms_path}#DPI", class: "teal-text" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Nebulizer", "#{dosage_forms_path}#Nebulizer", class: "teal-text" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "Nasal Spray", "#{dosage_forms_path}#Nasal-Spray", class: "teal-text" %></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-image-area w35">
        <%= image_tag "research-and-development/quality-system", alt: "alttext", class: "card-image w65" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area w65">
        <div class="card-text">
          <h4 class="text-larger text-bold teal-text">Quality System</h4>
          <p>Our quality team will ensure that all R&D activities are compliant with relevant regulations in China, USA, and Europe.</p>
          <ul class="bulleted-list">
            <li>Analytical method development and validation</li>
            <li>Establish specifications</li>
            <li>Manage the quality of suppliers of raw materials and packaging materials</li>
            <li>Successfully pass inspections conducted by authorities and customer audits to ensure all documents ready for Regulatory Submissions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
